357
00:18:47,994 --> 00:18:50,834
So unless you want
to get into trouble...

358
00:19:05,144 --> 00:19:06,944
Professor:
Kara?

359
00:19:06,946 --> 00:19:08,146
Kara?

360
00:19:08,148 --> 00:19:11,848
Have you made a decision
