I asking someone else?

362
00:19:14,954 --> 00:19:18,194
Yeah, I can do it.

363
00:20:14,780 --> 00:20:21,390
Wow. You look spectacular.

364
00:20:23,188 --> 00:20:24,858
Shall we?

365
00:20:34,366 --> 00:20:35,666
