Sure.

369
00:20:58,023 --> 00:20:59,963
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

370
00:21:03,328 --> 00:21:05,398
So...

371
00:21:05,398 --> 00:21:07,268
So...

372
00:21:07,267 --> 00:21:09,697
Shall we
take it upstairs?

373
00:21:11,370 --> 00:21:14,410
