the hottest guy ever.

402
00:24:32,905 --> 00:24:37,135
And then when you open them,
it's all over.

403
00:24:41,413 --> 00:24:43,113
Okay,
so what's going on?
What's the latest?

404
00:24:43,115 --> 00:24:46,415
Well, I just applied
for an internship.

405
00:24:46,419 --> 00:24:49,419
