441
00:26:24,350 --> 00:26:25,720
Oh, hi.

442
00:26:25,718 --> 00:26:28,148
Something wrong?
You sound upset.

443
00:26:28,154 --> 00:26:29,524
Oh, nothing.

444
00:26:29,522 --> 00:26:30,852
I just can't get
my car to start.

445
00:26:30,856 --> 00:26:32,886
Obviously
you're going to need

446
00:26:32,892 --> 00:26:34,692
