456
00:27:11,597 --> 00:27:13,327
I've got
a paper to write

457
00:27:13,332 --> 00:27:14,902
and a test to study for.

458
00:27:14,900 --> 00:27:15,930
Okay.

459
00:27:15,935 --> 00:27:18,065
