with his medical bills.

487
00:28:37,149 --> 00:28:38,979
You would do that?

488
00:28:38,984 --> 00:28:40,354
Sure.

489
00:28:40,352 --> 00:28:41,952
It was $80,000?

490
00:28:41,954 --> 00:28:43,624
It's no problem.

491
00:28:43,622 --> 00:28:45,492
Oh, my God.
Come here.

492
00:29:01,039 --> 00:29:02,909
